taniko
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an ornamental border or band
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: sometimes refers to the mat, not just its border
